    "description": "Join the Zepto South Asia Partners family as a SEO Specialist in Bhopal. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Zepto South Asia Partners:\nZepto South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zepto South Asia Partners!",
